<p>
    <strong>From the college:</strong>
    <i>Dordt College grants college credit for AP Exam scores of 3 or higher. A maximum of 30 credits of credit by examination through CLEP, AP or other college-level examinations will be accepted toward a degree at Dordt College.</i>
    <br/>
    For more information, <a href="http://www.dordt.edu/services_support/registrar/ap.shtml" target="_blank" title="Opens a new window">view the credit policy on this college's website</a>.
</p>

